cs.CR, cs.NI, cs.DL, cs.SI, cs.CY

This paper deals with the issue of fake content in the BitTorrent ecosystem, which is related to computer security (cs.CR) and network infrastructure (cs.NI). The authors also propose a new detection tool (FakeDetector) which involves machine learning techniques (cs.DL) and could potentially have an impact on cybersecurity (cs.SI) and cybercrime (cs.CY).
